reviews.text: Prices for lunch specials are reasonable. Food quality was quite good. Service is ok. Curry beef noodle tasted good except there was very little beef in it - 3 thin pieces of beef, all fit into a table spoon. We asked the waiter if this is normal and he said the amount was correct. Curry chicken rice on the other hand had plenty of tender chicken and tasted great. It’s located right next to the UA Cinema. A good choice for a quick meal before or after a movie.

Macau food is getting less in HK. We used to have Macau food when i was small. This new restaurant is letting me to refresh my memory to have Macau curry. But I can tell this restaurant give me another impression with the BBQ pork. I recommend to order the pork and also their curry. Macau egg tart you won’t miss it.

Really good Macanese food! But I agree with most reviews here, the service can be better. There is a lot of miscommunication amongst the staff. However, it does not change the fact the food is really good and I'd highly recommend the tarts too. The Pork Chop Bun with Chorizo is really good. The Portuguese influence is also nice!
Not bad, handcrafted beer is nice!
Got their signature baked chicken rice - the chicken and potatoes were stale. Also extremely bad attitude from the manager

result.name: 小島澳門菜

reviews.text:
暫時未去澳門 食個葡國菜懷念一下吧🤭
這間餐廳在時代廣場13樓 位置也易找的
去到的時候已經很多人 幸好等一會兒就有位

我們也快手快腳地下單 怕太多人要等太久
但上菜比我想像中快很多[惊恐][惊恐]
極速上菜是如何練成的🤭

·芝士蒜蓉包 HKD$48
鬆脆的蒜蓉包 從小到大都很喜歡食的
看到有就一定點這個 這個一上菜要即食🐥

·咖哩豬扒飯 HKD$118
咖哩味道不太辣 咖哩汁用來拌飯一流[色]
錦上添花的食物 很快被我們食清光🤣🤣

·奶黃流心葡撻 HKD$18
一切開裡面的奶黃就不停流出來
其實已攤放到最後才食 想不到還是流心[色]
新口味的葡撻沒有令我失望 很開心耶~

·焦糖葡撻 HKD$14
這個也是新口味的葡撻 味道比較香一點
因為無糖是很香的食材 配搭食物是棒棒噠

·玫瑰堂 HKD$68
這杯飲品紅酒/伏特加/雜莓/橙汁/7起
多款飲品食材所調製而成的果酒
味道比較容易入口 我很喜歡飲這個[色][色]

·荔枝梳打 HKD$42
味道不太甜剛剛好  顏色有點漸變的感覺🤤
梳打飲品食到口乾飲一口真的很爽

不用去澳門，估不到時代廣場都有一間裝修漂亮澳門菜，選了精選小島拼盤，比想像中大份，2人剛剛好，最好吃是辣肉腸松露芝士脆多士，下面有一片烤脆肉瓜，口感脆之中有濕潤。 
小島奶皇葡撻 有流心喎! 甜度較濃。
鮮橙檸檬葡撻 相反感覺很清新有檸檬和橙皮香味。
飲品選了1杯雞尾酒 Macau Tower ，很漂亮粉藍色的。會再來吃很有水準!

Prices for lunch specials are reasonable. Food quality was quite good. Service is ok. Curry beef noodle tasted good except there was very little beef in it - 3 thin pieces of beef, all fit into a table spoon. We asked the waiter if this is normal and he said the amount was correct. Curry chicken rice on the other hand had plenty of tender chicken and tasted great. It’s located right next to the UA Cinema. A good choice for a quick meal before or after a movie.
與朋友來聚舊了，叫了小島拼盤和點小吃，味道不錯，地方環境用小磚子設計，很有澳門味道。
服務很好，細心，訂位時預先講好無BB椅，食物味道也很好，如食物種類多些會更好

reviews.text: It's an eye candy. There's a lot of high end brand, so make sure to bring a lot of money. One of the best place to have a shopping spree

The Time Square of Hong Kong, nice ambience with tons of stores! Movie theater, nice big supermarket nearby and a skip away from a wet mart. Literally has everything. They usually do seasonal events at the front which is pretty interesting.
Very popular shopping centre. Great place to spend time
Shopping center in Wan Chai. Not the fanciest of fanciest, but pretty good brands and not too busy.
The age is showing on the exterior, but the stores stay relevant. Still a great place to get all your shopping done.
